             was indicted for <rs id="t18130407-33-off187" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130407-33-off187" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130407-33-off187" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t18130407-33-cd188" type="crimeDate">30th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130407-33-off187 t18130407-33-cd188"></join>, about the hour of two in the night, being in the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130407-33-victim347" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
                           Sharpe
                        <interp inst="t18130407-33-victim347" type="surname" value="Sharpe"></interp>
