                  ; a pocket-book, value 6 d. and fifteen shillings, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18130407-33-person350">
                        Charles 
                        Sharpe
                     <interp inst="t18130407-33-person350" type="surname" value="Sharpe"></interp>
