                        <interp inst="t18130407-33-person350" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  ; and that he did afterwards, about the same hour, in the night, burglariously break the said dwelling-house, in order to get out of it
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130407-33-person351">
                  CHARLES 
                  SHARPE
               <interp inst="t18130407-33-person351" type="surname" value="SHARPE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130407-33-person351" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
